flowchart TD
    A[Student logs in] --> B[System checks required profile fields]
    B --> C{Profile complete?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Go to Student Dashboard]
    C -->|No| E[Redirect to Profile Edit]
    E --> F[Student fills required fields]
    F --> G{Valid?}
    G -->|No| H[Show validation errors]
    G -->|Yes| I[Save profile]
    I --> D
